WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:15.026
Heoi anō, i tupu ake au i roto i tētahi wāhi e kīhia ana ko Tautoro,

2
00:00:15.026 --> 00:00:22.022
ko tēnei wāhi kei te tonga o Kaikohe, ko Kaikohe tō mātou tāone rahi.

3
00:00:22.022 --> 00:00:28.061
I tupu ake hoki au i roto i te kāinga e kōrerohia ana te reo,

4
00:00:28.061 --> 00:00:34.050
i tupu ake au i roto i te hapori e kōrerohia ana te reo.

5
00:00:34.050 --> 00:00:38.058
Nō reira, me pēnei pea taku kōrero mai i taku

6
00:00:38.058 --> 00:00:43.096
nō Wītanga mai ki tēnei ao tae noa ki tēnei rā ko taku reo tonu.

7
00:00:43.096 --> 00:00:51.085
Te...te reo i kaingākauhia e au, ae

8
00:00:51.085 --> 00:01:05.047
Kia kaha ō tātou rangatahi, mātua rangatahi.

9
00:01:05.047 --> 00:01:12.081
Kia kaha ō tātou mātua rangatahi ki te whāngai i te reo ki ō rātou tamariki,

10
00:01:12.081 --> 00:01:18.037
ngā mea puta mai ānei i ngā kura kaupapa ngā mea puta mai ānei i ngā whare wānanga.

11
00:01:18.037 --> 00:01:26.005
Ehara i te mea kāhore e mahi ana te mahi i tēnei wā ngākaunui ana au ki ngā momo mahi e mahia ana e

12
00:01:26.005 --> 00:01:36.022
ngā mātua rangatahi nei, ko tētahi me whakahua ake au i tana ingoa.

13
00:01:36.022 --> 00:01:46.042
Ko taku tamaiti ko Scotty Morrison, he tamaiti ū rāua tahi ki te reo me ō rāua hoa.

14
00:01:46.042 --> 00:01:49.003
Ehara ko rāua, engari ko ō rāua hoa

15
00:01:49.003 --> 00:01:55.097
mā te hanga i tētahi hapori, i waenga i ō hoa,

16
00:01:55.097 --> 00:01:59.030
whāngaihia, whakatōhia te kākano ki reira.

17
00:01:59.030 --> 00:02:04.003
Hei reira ka kite koe i te... i te reo e tupu ana.

18
00:02:04.003 --> 00:02:09.074
Nō reira, tō tātou reo Māori mā, tiakina.

19
00:02:09.074 --> 00:02:16.063
Tō tātou reo kāhore i homai mō te kore noa iho.

20
00:02:16.063 --> 00:02:20.042
E ai ki taku pāpā, kaua e noho noa iho, kaua e matapiko.

21
00:02:20.042 --> 00:02:26.019
ki tō reo, haere, whāngaihia i a rātou e hiakai mai ana.

22
00:02:26.019 --> 00:02:30.080
Ki te hunga kāhore e hiakai mai ana.

23
00:02:30.080 --> 00:02:54.033
whakapaetia ētahi mahi e taea ai e koe te hopu ō rātou hinengaro e tahuri mai ai ki te reo
